<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nouveau message de contact</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .message-details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .message-details div { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
        .message-content { white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #7f8c8d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Nouveau message de contact</h1>

    <p>Vous venez de recevoir un nouveau message de contact :</p>

    <div class="message-details">
        <div><span class="label">Nom :</span> {{ contact.lastname }}</div>
        <div><span class="label">Prénom :</span> {{ contact.firstname }}</div>
        <div><span class="label">Email :</span> <a href="mailto:{{ contact.mail }}">{{ contact.mail }}</a></div>
        {% if contact.tel %}
            <div><span class="label">Téléphone :</span> {{ contact.tel }}</div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <p><span class="label">Message :</span></p>
    <div class="message-content">
        {{ contact.message }}
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
